Summary of Amendments Adopted by House
The Committee Amendments Proposed by House Committee on Administration of
Criminal Justice to the original bill:
1. Change the "Dept. of Public Safety and Corrections, in conjunction with La.
State Police" to "law enforcement agencies responsible for investigating hit-and-
run driving offenses".
2. Provide a definition for "La. Law Enforcement Telecommunications System
(LLETS)".
3. Require law enforcement agencies investigating a hit-and-run driving offense to
use LLETS to disseminate information.
